        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your blood consumes arcane magic. Whenever you successfully save against a foe's harmful spell or magical effect, you gain temporary Hit Points equal to the spell's rank or equal to the level if the magical effect isn't a spell (double the number of temporary Hit Points you gain if the spell or trait is arcane). You gain these temporary Hit Points before the effect is resolved, and they last until the end of your next turn.</p>"
